quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  32,23,"Gom…óii Men okkii Muusaa Deftere nden, - wata a wonu e sikke e fii hawroygol e makko -, Men wa…ói nde …óoworde …ďi…ó…ďe Israa'iila …ďen"
  32,24,"Men wa…ói e ma…ď…ďe ardii…ďe, …óowiroo…ďe (yim…ďe …ďen) yamiroore Amen, nde …ďe mu√Ī√Īinoo, …ďe woni yananaa…ďe e Aayeeje Amen …óen"
  32,25,"Pellet, Joomi maa, ko Kanko senndoyta hakkunde ma…ď…ďe, √Ďalnde Darngal, e kon ko …ďe lurraynoo e fii mun"
  32,26,"E fee√Īanaali …ďe, no foti …óuu…óude e ko Men halki ado ma…ď…ďe e gire, hi…ďe yaha e ko…óooli ma…ď…ďe? Pellet, no e …óum, tasakuyeeji ! E …ďee haqqiltaa"
  32,27,"E …ďe yi'aali, wonnde Me…óen soggira ndiyam …óam ka leydi hokkundi, Men yaltinira …óam remuru, ndu neemoraa…ói ma…ď…ďe e kam…ďe √Īaamata e mun? E …ďe yi'ataa"
  32,28,"Hi…ďe wi'a: \"Ko honnde tuma woni ngal uddital, si on laatike goongu…ďe"
  32,29,"Maaku: \"√Ďalnde uddial ngal, ko heefer…ďe …ďen gom…óinoyta nafoytaa…ďe, wanaa kam…ďe woni nennantee…ďe"
  32,30,"∆äuurno …ďe, ha…ď…ďito-…óaa. Kam…ďe kan, ko …ďe ha…ď…ďitii…ďe (lepte)"